    "The absence of genes in one of the two annotations was investigated manually with the BLAST algorithm integrated into Persephone.",
    "Annotated genes found to be part of transposable elements were excluded from the analysis.",
    "Presence of the 135-Mb L3 haplotype block on chromosome 1D in wheat landraces.",
    "The presence of the 135-Mb L3 haplotype block was manually confirmed in 12 out of the 126 wheat landraces (Supplementary Table 16).",
